      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KINGSBRAE SARAH (2) was impressive last time, posting an effortless 5.5 lengths win in taking a Maiden in 17.25 and a new Best time this course and distance. Expected to push the clock again. NEON DRIFT (3) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. Was out of the placings last time (22.43) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 7 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. NICKY ACES (1) crossed over from out wide but caught the leaders turning before drawing clear to score (17.50) at this track in a Grade 5 over 300m. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. DOMINANT XENA (4) is new to this track but should be in the mix.",
